('chunk_1a222619065b77207b','file_8378b145fc1fad06fd','physics.md','Command-Term Question Bank','1. **State** the difference between distance and displacement. (Criterion A — recall)
2. **Calculate** the acceleration of a car that speeds up from 8 m/s to 20 m/s in 4 s. (Criterion A — apply)
